{"tid":53650,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"習近平透露 可忍受中國GDP低於6.5%","createTime":"2016-12-24T22:44:48.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-25T02:59:23.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"963dcfb03a724585c58b3fcb46bb1b6975041e13","tid":53650,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T22:44:48.000Z","msg":"2016年12月23日20:54 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/ReNews/20161223/640_d44e790bef823b8444c1a94645158f38.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwimg.edgesuite.net%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20161223%2F640_d44e790bef823b8444c1a94645158f38.jpg&h=7792be84&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n法新社 <br />\n<br />\n知悉內情的人士向財經媒體彭博披露，中國國家主席習近平本週與中央財經領導小組開會時，示意可接受經濟成長率低於官方目標底線6.5%，考量到中國負債規模持續擴大以及川普（Donald Trump）當選美國總統後不安定的全球情勢，擔心若決意死守6.5%，可能反而釀成太大風險。 <br />\n<br />\n中國官方去年年末發佈「十三五規劃」時，明訂到2020年為止經濟年均成長率底線是6.5%，習近平當時也表示，未來5年經濟成長率不應低於6.5%。隨後部分經濟學家對此提出批評，認為這可能促使決策官員為達目標而採取危及金融穩定性的行動，IMF（International Monetary Fund，國際貨幣基金）也建議中國應降低經濟成長目標。 <br />\n<br />\n不過，透露消息的知情人士表示，參與本週會議的領導層官員均同意，只要就業持穩，中國經濟可望保持穩定，只是成長步調將減緩。（劉利貞／綜合外電報導） <br />\n<br />\nlink:<a href=\"http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/finance/20161223/1019546/%E7%BF%92%E5%A4%A7%E5%A4%A7%E9%AC%86%E5%8F%A3%E4%BA%86%EF%BC%81%E5%8F%AF%E5%BF%8D%E5%8F%97%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F%E6%88%90%E9%95%B7%E4%BD%8E%E6%96%BC6.5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Ffinance%2F20161223%2F1019546%2F%25E7%25BF%2592%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E9%25AC%2586%25E5%258F%25A3%25E4%25BA%2586%25EF%25BC%2581%25E5%258F%25AF%25E5%25BF%258D%25E5%258F%2597%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E7%25B6%2593%25E6%25BF%259F%25E6%2588%2590%25E9%2595%25B7%25E4%25BD%258E%25E6%2596%25BC6.5&d=NfLHfgbwHVIQMAjoJl73sksIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=70fc2892\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/finance/20161223/1019546/%E7%BF%92%E5%A4%A7%E5%A4%A7%E9%AC%86%E5%8F%A3%E4%BA%86%EF%BC%81%E5%8F%AF%E5%BF%8D%E5%8F%97%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F%E6%88%90%E9%95%B7%E4%BD%8E%E6%96%BC6.5</a>"},{"pid":"f5ec6af1281b7d4911e53dd018ffc9bdd18cc547","tid":53650,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T23:24:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04ac3ba8f510f35f4bef58a616af110188f3d197","tid":53650,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T23:30:56.000Z","msg":"嘩 雜種你講到可以控制到咁喎<br />\n早講啦 咁我唔洗返工就gdp go go go<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0360069f71fcda3b108447b32e69b756184a94f","tid":53650,"uid":351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T23:50:14.000Z","msg":"反正跌嘅係嗰班不嬲底過6.5嘅地底泥 關官商大財團咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75d7bd57a0c246562fbd610ca632e5e8ae4cda7e","tid":53650,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T02:48:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fa80087f47d175c396539b8dead6d820b5c563d","tid":53650,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T02:49:25.000Z","msg":"反正條數都係做,你做到8,9%都無人會再質疑你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fbfb31e7291efd0ba87c42535e8d33acef4aa90","tid":53650,"uid":44454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T02:59:23.000Z","msg":"開放返報銷制度，GDP升幾多都得啦，有日係深圳地鐵站，見到有人攞D唔要嘅冲值收據，有成幾十張，最少都有成千蚊，如果報銷到，GDP又GoGoGo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}